# Prolance

- **Auth**: Supabase Auth + JWT; use [`AuthService`](client/lib/core/services/auth_service.dart). Do not reintroduce password-in-SharedPreferences auth.
- **Routing**: [`GoRouter`](client/lib/core/navigation/app_router.dart) + `context.go` / `context.push`. Public routes: `/`, `/onboarding`, `/login`, `/register`, `/forgot-password`.
- **Data**: Prefer Supabase tables in [`supabase/migrations/`](supabase/migrations/) with RLS. Job reads go through [`SupabaseJobRepository`](client/lib/core/repositories/supabase_job_repository.dart).
- **Escrow**: Business logic in [`PaymentService`](client/lib/core/services/payment_service.dart); optional Edge Function [`supabase/functions/escrow`](supabase/functions/escrow).
- **Tests**: `cd client && flutter test`; widget tests must call [`bootstrap()`](client/lib/main.dart) via `setUpAll` and use `SharedPreferences.setMockInitialValues({})`.
- **Monorepo**: Flutter mobile in [`client/`](client/); Next.js (landing + admin) in [`web/`](web/); backend in [`supabase/`](supabase/).
